           zùstane v cmmi (Computer Modern math italic) a index "1" rovnì¾
           zùstane v cmr (Computer Modern Roman).
  Analogicky dal¹í písmové sady:
           ctimes   ... Times-Roman
           cbookman ... Bookman
           cncent   ... NewCenturySchlbk
           chelvet  ... Helvetica
           cavantga ... AvantGarde-Book
